{"id": 2011, "genre": 1000, "title": "那些专为“专为懒人”设计的功能/产品，你觉着到底为啥用不上？", "description": "滴，懒人卡。（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 10047, "comment_count": 37, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171114162744xwfIkgX7eWY9iQvT.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-14T17:00:58Z", "questions": [{"id": 3280, "title": "那些专为“专为懒人”设计的功能/产品，你觉着到底为啥用不上？", "content": "那些专为“专为懒人”设计的功能/产品，你到底为啥用不上？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 248487, "content": "搞合并同类项，省掉某些本来也不麻烦的工具/步骤，比如喷水牙刷啥的", "image": "img/option/option/20171114164009JxZTtM5WNcCOj4FB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248488, "content": "强调便携，但……为啥我要随身携带懒得用的东西", "image": "img/option/option/20171114165639C4jpbFWxBGec9gNz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248490, "content": "化简为繁，比如把每一个料理步骤拆开来搞出花儿的各式懒人厨具", "image": "img/option/option/20171114164144GhuvDZz4dBi9ECNl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248567, "content": "意外且多余的多功能混搭，兼任拖把的拖鞋什么的", "image": "img/option/option/20171114170405TqZUyK3IOavBPoAw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248568, "content": "品质可疑，一百效合一懒人面霜，多大胆才敢往脸上抹", "image": "img/option/option/20171114164423Ok2uKMsxr0I6dtNW.png", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248574, "content": "有些不能省的事儿也要帮我省，比如躺着赚钱懒人理财，不敢用", "image": "img/option/option/201711141703375EjuC3WyqRxzHwNU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248575, "content": "懒人听书，网文鸡汤书大全，听了坏脑子", "image": "img/option/option/20171114170316Izpx5wKy2Os6V9cC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 248577, "content": "搞错目标受众，懒人收纳架收纳盒什么的，真懒人并不想收纳只想随手扔", "image": "img/option/option/20171114170119A34v0ZypDuRNTYKB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}